{
  "title": "dense brazilian rice bake",
  "description": "this dish features a unique combination of poppy seeds, onion, and spices that will leave your taste buds wanting more. it's a hearty and satisfying braziel dish perfect for any meal",
  "cuisine": "brazilian",
  "diet": [
    "gluten-free",
